Class DeliveryRequest

java.lang.Object
com.pld.agile.model.entity.DeliveryRequest
public class DeliveryRequest extends Object
The DeliveryRequest class represents a delivery request, which includes a delivery address and an assigned courier. This class provides methods to retrieve and update the delivery address and courier.
